videos.description: Kentucky's Kavosiey Smoke goes right through the defense for the 35-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Smoke breaks through the line for Kentucky TD) 2020/09/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Smoke breaks through the line for Kentucky TD

videos.description: Seth Williams gets down to the Kentucky 1 yard line, which sets up a D.J. Williams touchdown a couple plays later.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Williams' big gain leads to Auburn TD) 2020/09/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williams' big gain leads to Auburn TD

videos.description: Auburn's Roger McCreary seems to get the 100-yard pick-six, but it's taken back due to a targeting penalty on the return.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Auburn’s 100-yard pick-6 taken away due to targeting) 2020/09/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Auburn's 100-yard pick-six taken away due to targeting

videos.description: Bo Nix throws a dart to wide receiver Seth Williams, who goes up and snags it, extending Auburn's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Auburn’s Williams soars in the air for the TD grab) 2020/09/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Auburn's Williams soars in the air for the TD grab

videos.description: Terry Wilson finds Akeem Hayes in the end zone for the eight-yard touchdown, cutting in to Auburn's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wilson ropes pass to Hayes for the Kentucky TD) 2020/09/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wilson ropes pass to Hayes for the Kentucky TD

videos.description: Bo Nix throws the fade to Seth Williams who reaches over the defender and hauls in the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Auburn’s Williams goes over the defender for the TD catch) 2020/09/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Auburn's Williams goes over the defender for the TD catch

videos.description: Auburn is not fooled by the fake punt as they tackle the punter for a loss of yards, then a couple plays later, Bo Nix finds Eli Stove for a 21-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Auburn stuffs the fake punt, then scores the TD) 2020/09/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Auburn stuffs the fake punt, then scores the TD

videos.description: Bo Nix impresses with two punts inside the 10-yard line, then he shows off his arm, throwing three touchdowns in Auburn's win over Kentucky.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Nix does it all with his arm … and his leg) 2020/09/26 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Nix does it all with his arm ... and his leg

videos.description: No. 8 Auburn standout WR Seth Williams leads the way with six catches and two touchdowns in a hard-fought 29-13 victory over No. 23 Kentucky.
videos.headline: Williams leads Auburn past tough UK squad

videos.description: The Tigers' Gus Malzahn says "third downs were the name of the game" after quarterback Bo Nix throws for three TDs in victory over Kentucky.
videos.headline: Auburn's Malzahn praises defense and play of Nix
